Line 1: Imports the Flutter material library.
Line 2-12: Imports all screen widgets from various feature directories (chat, contacts, auth, home, profile, settings, splash, history).
Line 14: Defines the static Routes class to centralize navigation logic.
Line 15: Creates a global key for the NavigatorState to enable contextless navigation.
